quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  10,11,WE LEW JU’AXHXHILU ELLAHU LILNNASI ESH-SHERRE ESTI’XHALEHUM BIL-HAJRI LEKUDIJE ‘ILEJHIM ‘EXHELUHUM FENEDHERUL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA FI TUGJANIHIM JA’MEHUNE
  10,12,WE ‘IDHA MESSEL-’INSANE ED-DURRU DA’ANA LIXHENBIHI ‘EW KA’IDÆN ‘EW KA’IMÆN FELEMMA KESHEFNA ‘ANHU DURREHU MERRE KE’EN LEM JED’UNA ‘ILA DURRIN MESSEHU KEDHALIKE ZUJJINE LILMUSRIFINE MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  10,13,WE LEKAD ‘EHLEKNAL-KURUNE MIN KABLIKUM LEMMA DHELEMU WE XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI WE MA KANU LIJU’UMINU KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-KAWMEL-MUXHRIMINE
  10,14,THUMME XHE’ALNAKUM HALA’IFE FIL-’ERDI MIN BA’DIHIM LINENDHURE KEJFE TA’MELUNE
  10,15,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUNA BEJJINATIN KALEL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA E’TI BIKUR’ANIN GAJRI HADHA ‘EW BEDDILHU KUL MA JEKUNU LI ‘EN ‘UBEDDILEHU MIN TILKA’I NEFSI ‘IN ‘ETTEBI’U ‘ILLA MA JUHA ‘ILEJJE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘IN ‘ASEJTU RABBI ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘A
  10,16,KUL LEW SHA’EL-LAHU MA TELEWTUHU ‘ALEJKUM WE LA ‘EDRAKUM BIHI FEKAD LEBITHTU FIKUM ‘UMURÆN MIN KABLIHI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  10,17,FEMEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘EW KEDHDHEBE BI’AJATIHI ‘INNEHU LA JUFLIHUL-MUXHRIMUNE
  10,18,WE JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JEDURRUHUM WE LA JENFA’UHUM WE JEKULUNE HA’UULA’ SHUFA’A’UUNA ‘INDEL-LAHI KUL ‘ETUNEBBI’UNEL-LAHE BIMA LA JA’LEMU FI ES-SEMAWATI WE LA FIL-’ERDI SUBHANEHU WE TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  10,19,WE MA KANE EN-NASU ‘ILLA ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN FAHTELEFU WE LEWLA KELIMETUN SEBEKAT MIN RABBIKE LEKUDIJE BEJNEHUM FIMA FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  10,20,WE JEKULUNE LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI FEKUL ‘INNEMAL-GAJBU LILLAHI FANTEDHIRU ‘INNI ME’AKUM MINEL-MUNTEDHIRINE
  10,21,WE ‘IDHA ‘EDHEKNA EN-NASE REHMETEN MIN BA’DI DERRA’E MESSET/HUM ‘IDHA LEHUM MEKRUN FI ‘AJATINA KULI ELLAHU ‘ESRA’U MEKRÆN ‘INNE RUSULENA JEKTUBUNE MA TEMKURUN
  10,22,HUWEL-LEDHI JUSEJJIRUKUM FIL-BERRI WEL-BEHRI HETTA ‘IDHA KUNTUM FIL-FULKI WE XHEREJNE BIHIM BIRIHIN TEJJIBETIN WE FERIHU BIHA XHA’ET/HA RIHUN ‘ASIFUN WE XHA’EHUMUL-MEWXHU MIN KULLI MEKANIN WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHUM ‘UHITE BIHIM DE’AW ELLAHE MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DIN
  10,23,FELEMMA ‘ENXHAHUM ‘IDHA HUM JEBGUNE FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNEMA BEGJUKUM ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIKUM META’AL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA THUMME ‘ILEJNA MERXHI’UKUM FENUNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  10,24,‘INNEMA METHELUL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA KEMA’IN ‘ENZELNAHU MINE ES-SEMA’I FAHTELETE BIHI NEBATUL-’ERDI MIMMA JE’KULU EN-NASU WEL-’EN’AM HETTA ‘IDHA ‘EHADHETIL-’ERDU ZUHRUFEHA WE EZZEJJENET WE DHENNE ‘EHLUHA ‘ENNEHUM KADIRUNE ‘ALEJHA ‘ETAHA ‘EMRUNA LEJLÆN ‘EW NEH
  10,25,WEL-LAHU JED’U ‘ILA DARI ES-SELAMI WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN